{"tid":1188400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(亮劍) 川普 : 還可對中国3000億美元產品加徵關稅","createTime":"2019-06-06T08:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T11:21:20.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c5c8f0a5f3160ae7070b3d6e1f8ad1b8e70035d3","tid":1188400,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:35:22.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普再度放話，表示他還可以對另外至少價值3,000億美元的中國輸美產品加徵關稅。<br />\n<br />\n川普6日在愛爾蘭登上空軍一號前往法國參加諾曼地登陸75周年紀念活動之前，對記者談到對中國的加徵關稅措施。<br />\n<br />\n川普說：「我們正在對2,500億美元（陸貨）徵收25%的關稅，而且我還可以對另外至少3,000億美元加徵關稅，我將在適當的時候那麼做。」<br />\n<br />\n川普還表示： 「我想中國太渴望達成協議了，我想墨西哥也太渴望達成協議了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/06/06/realtime/6398648.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F06%2F06%2Frealtime%2F6398648.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26exp%3D3600&h=542ed016&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖／美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3856936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F3856936&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgoICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=2536a8fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3856936</a>"},{"pid":"eda4e6a0687524930011ccd4d34619653ac6aa14","tid":1188400,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"中國：我們還有稀土<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2853985/org/88e72140f0d6b3dc1fc917156eabfcfa.jpg/xYidq_dJ_a_qo2AjNNlFLgJstoqApcqWBQgjywUII8s?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2853985%2Forg%2F88e72140f0d6b3dc1fc917156eabfcfa.jpg%2FxYidq_dJ_a_qo2AjNNlFLgJstoqApcqWBQgjywUII8s%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=1de2ae93&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27e405ed6601df748c8d